{"tid":1739221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"狗都係動物，狗畀人淋冰水，都會有低溫症㗎...","createTime":"2019-11-19T13:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T15:08:22.000Z","uid":284284,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7446b5177bea0aebbe2725e512096ac0129d14aa","tid":1739221,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:40:40.000Z","msg":"今個星期, 天氣轉冷, 得16度ja!<br />\n<br />\n如果狗隻禽獸呢d畜生有火光伴隨,  其實係會感覺溫暖㗎<br />\n但係如果大地降臨冰水, 照頭淋, 仲要on duty企足最少八個小時<br />\n呢d畜生狗隻都會凍到有低溫症㗎 <br />\n<br />\n作為一個成日口乾又怕熱嘅汽車維修員，帶備大量冰水出街，其實係好合理嘅 !<br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n當年納粹德軍第一次慘敗, 最後輸到成個納粹德國畀殲滅<br />\n唔係死喺蘇聯軍手中, 唔係死喺英美聯軍手中<br />\n而係死喺西伯利亞大自然嘅冰天雪地手中......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9464a2af5ff455c498407a2b7126a3fcc179128c","tid":1739221,"uid":251111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cafc15e5ce659a884535780bac96855b6fba216","tid":1739221,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da90ede9d868c95906c72bc262755621e361aa7d","tid":1739221,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bfc78cfc13caaf86d783d67e1ef5cf36143b41","tid":1739221,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gi